# Project Overview

This project is a stock market application that provides users with real-time stock data, interactive charts, and a customizable dashboard. Users can register and log in to access personalized features, such as creating a customized dashboard with various widgets, searching and filtering stocks, and viewing graphical representations of stock trends. The application is designed for web platforms, ensuring a seamless experience for users.

# Setup and Installation Instructions

## Prerequisites
- Node.js installed (version X.X.X)
- NPM installed (version X.X.X)

## Steps
Clone the repository.
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-project.git
Navigate to the project directory: cd your-project
                                    npm install
Run the application.:  npm start


Features List and Descriptions

User Authentication :
Description: Enables users to register and log in to the application.
Implementation: Utilizes a secure authentication mechanism to manage user accounts.

Real-Time Stock Data:
Description: Fetches and displays real-time stock data using external APIs.
Implementation: Utilizes APIs such as IEX Cloud to retrieve up-to-date stock information.

Interactive Charts:
Description: Presents graphical representations of stock trends for better analysis.
Implementation: Uses charting libraries like Chart.js to create interactive and visually appealing charts.

Customizable Dashboard:
Description: Allows users to add, remove, and rearrange widgets on their dashboard.
Implementation: I have added a checkbox for that, if the check box is checked, the search will appear/disappear.

Search and Filter:
Description: Provides users with the ability to search for specific stocks and apply filters.
Implementation: Search Functionality is added to filter records. 

Mobile Responsiveness:
Description: Ensures a seamless user experience on both web and mobile platforms.
Implementation: Utilizes responsive design principles and React Native for mobile compatibility.

User Settings;
Description: Offers customizable user settings such as theme toggles and notification preferences.
Implementation: Stores user preferences in a secure manner and provides an intuitive settings interface.
